<section id="faq" class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Frequently asked</span>
      <h2>Questions, answered straight.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">What does it cost?</summary>
        <div class="faq-a">Website builds start at $3,500 for a 5-page Shopify or Astro site. VOIP phone systems start at $45/line/month all-in. Custom dashboards start at $1,000 to build, priced up from there based on scope and integrations. Ongoing SEO runs $500–$1,500/month depending on scope. Everything is scoped and quoted up front &mdash; no surprises.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">Do you really replace my phone system?</summary>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes &mdash; and for most small operators, we cut the phone bill in half or better. Modern VOIP handles everything legacy PBX does (auto-attendant, call routing, hold music, voicemail) plus things it can't (voicemail-to-email, SMS from your business number, mobile softphone). We port your existing number so customers never notice the switch.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">What does a custom dashboard actually pull in?</summary>
        <div class="faq-a">Whatever you use. Common integrations: Shopify, Square, Toast, DoorDash, Uber Eats, GA4, Google Search Console, QuickBooks, Homebase, and inventory systems. We build it around your business &mdash; not a template. You get one screen that answers "how did we do today?" in under 10 seconds.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">How long until my site is live?</summary>
        <div class="faq-a">4–6 weeks from signed proposal to launch. Two weeks of discovery, three weeks of build, one week of polish and go-live. Phone system switchover is usually a 1-week window once numbers are ported.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">I already have a website &mdash; do you do improvements?</summary>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. We start every engagement with a free audit. Sometimes the right move is a rebuild; sometimes it's a restructure and SEO overhaul on what you have. We'll tell you honestly either way.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">Do you work with franchises or chains?</summary>
        <div class="faq-a">No. We're built for independent operators and single-location businesses. If you're a regional chain or multi-unit group, we'll refer you to someone better suited.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

